{"tid":2114574,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"20分鐘都尖沙嘴 背山面海 平過居屋都冇人講？","createTime":"2020-07-19T02:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T08:46:43.000Z","uid":351218,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdb9521675cad0cfe20d0958d4c39bcbc82c9c3","tid":2114574,"uid":351218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"豪景花園真係香港嘅後花園 渣車20分鐘到尖沙嘴 10分鐘到荃灣 塞車就預多10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然附近得間百佳 2間餐廳 不過我唔需要附近有便利店 藥房之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去荃灣做Gym再買送再渣10分鐘返屋企不知幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清靜嘅屋企好有度假Feel 唔洗7球都700尺Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車位又多又平<br />\n重點係附近冇大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平過居屋 實際上係私樓 唔洗補地價 又有度假Feel嘅海景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夏天又涼爽過市區好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁抵屌 竟然冇人買？<br />\n其實工作地點穩定 養到架車 真係強烈建議買 但係廁所有時要整下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS 共產黨嘅明日大嶼計劃係豪景花園隔離整個過海隧道 不過睇怕都Delay 20年先起好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇40年後爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bde69a40077c270356183a0064ef96cdbc4195","tid":2114574,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"退休住ok ge😂"},{"pid":"766927149314edbec4763a78f37f8550c38940b4","tid":2114574,"uid":185013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"間超巿好可怕架，可以全個架的野清晒"},{"pid":"7f3697b473739c7c26ec6ee8d2bf09503933ba78","tid":2114574,"uid":156542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"個屋苑 無乜人住㗎 <br />\n好恐怖"},{"pid":"ad9aec093169c0703d419e14a01938e900232fa9","tid":2114574,"uid":195269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"樓主做乜自爆自己住邊，近排想賣樓？"},{"pid":"d288956569d7a1679353868f92f08bb00ce27c45","tid":2114574,"uid":281034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"揸車梗係方便，不過去到市區冇位泊，都係搭返車，完。"},{"pid":"4033986249ff4a1717cb4be8d9580e55c9a7da56","tid":2114574,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華懋陣營昨亦呈上於青龍頭豪景花園風水洞起出一塊約2呎&times;2呎泥水鋼板，上有一些紅色粗線條圖案</blockquote><br />\n堅係有靈界洞穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4711d9f0912649c9426fa5d19c474d3f2f7e0fb","tid":2114574,"uid":298385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"師兄咩鐘數出荃灣可以泊到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bc7078f6a092c574a0bfcc94e18cf91a679c9d","tid":2114574,"uid":351218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"766927149314edbec4763a78f37f8550c38940b4","tid":2114574,"uid":185013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"間超巿好可怕架，可以全個架的野清晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"長州先係播 好少會清曬 至少我要買嘅嘢都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de132ba136159cf198c1a3f7f7e32f68c0996db9","tid":2114574,"uid":343754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:47:13.000Z","msg":"住豪景不如住深井<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328e3914bd95df3977435650cda42d5886c2e121","tid":2114574,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de132ba136159cf198c1a3f7f7e32f68c0996db9","tid":2114574,"uid":343754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:47:13.000Z","msg":"住豪景不如住深井<img src=\"/asset